> In 4th Gear on a stock tranny, what are the RPMs for 55, 60, 65, 70 and
> 75 MPH? I want to know how high I am revving the engine at highway speeds
> and figure out the best speed to cruise at without frying the valves or
> overstressing the engine. I think the vanagon stock engine works best at
